a.n: Wkf championships 2016 montpelier, france, 08.05.2016 sunday morning session

p.d: The 2016 WKF World Karate Championships bring together the most established karate practitioners on the planet to decide who is the best of the best. Emanating from Montpelier, France, this edition of the World Karate Championships will decide the winners in different weight categories for both men and women in the kumite (fighting) portion.
